{"tid":2431867,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英專訪：沿用現時選舉制度或有外國傀儡入治港班子","createTime":"2021-03-04T02:44:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T15:31:46.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"df3f13e11346546bdbb4e902d96cf46c8891f927","tid":2431867,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T02:44:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1578668_1_20210304102227.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1578668_1_20210304102227.jpg&h=c8eed6a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁振英表示，要完善選舉制度，堵塞漏洞，確保最後的選舉結果做到愛國者治港。（政協大會新聞中心網路視頻採訪間拍攝提供）<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n正在北京準備出席全國兩會的梁振英，以視像訪問方式接受本台專訪，他強調愛國者治港的原則和目標完全是天經地義。<br />\n<br />\n他批評香港有立法會議員跑到外國，要求對方制裁自己國家和香港，形容此行為聳人聽聞，不愛國家，亦危害國家利益。雖然香港已落實《香港國安法》，但梁振英認為，若果香港沿用現時的選舉制度及方式，這批人可能在下一屆仍會當選，出現外國的傀儡進入治港班子，這是絕不能接受，因此需要完善選舉制度，堵塞漏洞，確保最後的選舉結果做到愛國者治港。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578668-20210304.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578668-20210304.htm&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX0BSGL744lGwoqCHTcH8MN0%3D&h=f3332079\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578668-20210304.htm&h=6999f7c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578668-20210304.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7434fd711a35b02825da75c19f4520dd445bc0d5","tid":2431867,"uid":14422,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T02:46:54.000Z","msg":"係唔係講緊全家都外國籍果個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X7jS9p5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX7jS9p5.png&h=cc2a8a68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d433b8a17035afe941a91271f85bbdb9cc90b16","tid":2431867,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20